              "name": "ClrType",
              "value": "System.String"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "description": "Query the API documentation index.\nQUERY SYNTAX:\n  Name searches (default): Require exact matches, case-insensitive\n  Content searches: Support full Lucene query syntax including:\n    - Wildcards: * (multiple chars), ? (single char)\n      Example: string* matches string, strings, stringify\n    - Fuzzy: ~ for similar terms\n      Example: roam~ matches foam, roams\n    - Boolean: AND, OR, NOT (must be uppercase)\n      Example: string AND utility\n    - Phrases: Use quotes for exact phrases\n      Example: \"strongly typed\"\n    \nSEARCH TYPES:\n  name      - Exact name match (default)\n  content   - Full-text search in documentation\n  namespace - Exact namespace match\n  id        - Exact member ID (e.g., T:System.String)\n  assembly  - Exact assembly name match",
      "hidden": false,
      "examples": [
        "query String",
        "query List<T>",
        "query string* --type content",
        "query utilit? --type content",
        "query tokenze~ --type content",
        "query \"extension methods\" --type content",
        "query string AND manipulation --type content",
        "query System.Collections.Generic --type namespace",
        "query T:System.String --type id --format json"
      ]
